Overview
The Department of Homeland Security (DHS) is responsible for
vital homeland and national defense missions across eight oper-
ational components. From providing border security to keeping the
flying public safe, to protecting our Nation’s key leadership, guard-
ing against cybersecurity threats to the country’s critical infra-
structure, and to responding to both natural and man-made disas-
