threats to surface transportation infrastructure become more ad-
vanced, TSA must equip itself and industry partners with tools
that support real-time risk mitigation across operational and infor-
mation technologies. TSA is encouraged to modernize and scale the
toolkit to allow TSA to automate cyber assurance functions, iden-
